    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for daily transportation. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few minor dings on the passenger side, and some fading in the paint on the hood. Inside, the cabin is clean but shows signs of regular use, including some wear on the driver's seat upholstery. Mechanically, the car starts reliably and drives well, though it may require routine maintenance soon to keep it in top shape. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for anyone needing a functional vehicle without the price tag of a newer model.",
